msgstr "Monks’ Suspension"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:4.1"
msgid "Kula­dūsaka­sikkhā­pada"
msgstr "13. The training rule on corrupters of families"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.180"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.314"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-ss.13.1"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1753"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.2"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anātha­piṇḍi­kassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

#. <span class="note" hidden>These were their names according to <span class="ref">Sp.3.613.26</span>, not Assaji and Punabbasu: “just Assaji and Punabbasuka,” <i lang="pli">assaji ceva punabbasuko ca</i>. By specifying “just,” the commentary understands the two names to refer to those two individuals and not to any group of followers they may have had. This is also clear from the text below, where a <i lang="pli">saṅghakamma</i> is performed against <i lang="pli">assajipunabbasukā bhikkhū</i>, which, due to the nature of <i lang="pli">saṅghakamma</i>, must mean the two monks and not any group led by them. See also <span class="ref">MS.1.1565</span>.</span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena assaji­pu­nabba­sukā nāma kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāsikā honti alajjino pāpabhikkhū."
msgstr "At that time the bad and shameless monks Assaji and Punabbasuka were staying at Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.4"
msgid "Te evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ ācaranti—"
msgstr "They engaged in these kinds of improper behavior:"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.5"
msgid "mālāvacchaṃ ropentipi ropāpentipi, siñcantipi siñcāpentipi, ocinantipi ocināpentipi, ganthentipi ganthāpentipi,"
msgstr "They planted flowering trees, watered and plucked them, and then tied the flowers together."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.6"
msgid "ekato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi, ubhato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi,"
msgstr "They made the flowers into garlands, garlands with stalks on one side and garlands with stalks on both sides."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.315"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.7"
msgid "mañjarikaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi, vidhūtikaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi, vaṭaṃsakaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi, āveḷaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi, uracchadaṃ karontipi kārāpentipi."
msgstr "They made flower arrangements, wreaths, ornaments for the head, ornaments for the ears, and ornaments for the chest. And they had others do the same."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.8"
msgid "Te kulitthīnaṃ kuladhītānaṃ kulakumārīnaṃ kulasuṇhānaṃ kuladāsīnaṃ ekato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, ubhato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, mañjarikaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, vidhūtikaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, vaṭaṃsakaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, āveḷaṃ harantipi harāpentipi, uracchadaṃ harantipi harāpentipi."
msgstr "They then took these things, or sent them, to the women, the daughters, the girls, the daughter-in-laws, and the female slaves of good families."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.9"
msgid "Te kulitthīhi kuladhītāhi kulakumārīhi kulasuṇhāhi kuladāsīhi saddhiṃ ekabhājanepi bhuñjanti, ekathālakepi pivanti,"
msgstr "They ate from the same plates as these women and drank from the same vessels."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.10"
msgid "ekāsanepi nisīdanti, ekamañcepi tuvaṭṭenti, ekattharaṇāpi tuvaṭṭenti, ekapāvuraṇāpi tuvaṭṭenti, ekattha­ra­ṇa­pāvu­raṇāpi tuvaṭṭenti,"
msgstr "They sat on the same seats as them, and they lay down on the same beds, the same mats, the same blankets, the same mats and blankets."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.11"
msgid "vikālepi bhuñjanti, majjampi pivanti, mālā­gandha­vi­lepa­nampi dhārenti,"
msgstr "They ate at the wrong time, drank alcohol, and used garlands, perfumes, and cosmetics."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.12"
msgid "naccantipi gāyantipi vādentipi lāsentipi,"
msgstr "They danced, sang, played instruments, and performed."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.13"
msgid "naccantiyāpi naccanti, naccantiyāpi gāyanti, naccantiyāpi vādenti, naccantiyāpi lāsenti, gāyantiyāpi naccanti, gāyantiyāpi gāyanti, gāyantiyāpi vādenti, gāyantiyāpi lāsenti, vādentiyāpi naccanti, vādentiyāpi gāyanti, vādentiyāpi vādenti, vādentiyāpi lāsenti, lāsentiyāpi naccanti, lāsentiyāpi gāyanti, lāsentiyāpi vādenti, lāsentiyāpi lāsenti;"
msgstr "While the women were dancing, singing, playing instruments, and performing, so would they."

#. </p><p><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.2"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.316"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.317"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.14"
msgid "aṭṭhapadepi kīḷanti, dasapadepi kīḷanti, ākāsepi kīḷanti, pari­hāra­pa­thepi kīḷanti, santikāyapi kīḷanti, khalikāyapi kīḷanti, ghaṭikāyapi kīḷanti, salāka­hat­thenapi kīḷanti, akkhenapi kīḷanti, paṅgacīrenapi kīḷanti, vaṅkakenapi kīḷanti, mokkhacikāyapi kīḷanti, ciṅgulakenapi kīḷanti, pattāḷhakenapi kīḷanti, rathakenapi kīḷanti, dhanukenapi kīḷanti, akkharikāyapi kīḷanti, manesikāyapi kīḷanti, yathāvajjenapi kīḷanti."
msgstr "They played various games: board games with eight or ten rows, imaginary board games, hopscotch, spillikins, dice games, tip-cat, painting-with-the-hand games, ball games, toy pipe games, toy plow games, turning somersaults, toy windmill games, toy measure games, toy chariot games, toy bow games, letter-guessing games, thought-guessing games, games of mimicking deformities."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.15"
msgid "Hatthismimpi sikkhanti, assasmimpi sikkhanti, rathasmimpi sikkhanti, dhanusmimpi sikkhanti, tharusmimpi sikkhanti,"
msgstr "They trained in elephant riding, in horsemanship, in carriage riding, in archery, in swordsmanship."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.16"
msgid "hatthissapi purato dhāvanti, assassapi purato dhāvanti, rathassapi purato dhāvantipi ādhāvantipi,"
msgstr "And they ran in front of elephants, in front of horses, and in front of carriages, and they ran backwards and forwards."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.17"
msgid "usseḷentipi, apphoṭentipi, nibbujjhantipi, muṭṭhīhipi yujjhanti,"
msgstr "They whistled, clapped their hands, wrestled, and boxed."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.318"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.18"
msgid "raṅgamajjhepi saṅghāṭiṃ pattharitvā naccakiṃ evaṃ vadanti—"
msgstr "They spread their outer robe on a stage and said to the dancing girls,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.19"
msgid "“idha, bhagini, naccassū”ti,"
msgstr "“Dance here, Sister,”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.20"
msgid "nalāṭikampi denti,"
msgstr "and they made gestures of approval."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:5.21"
msgid "vividhampi anācāraṃ ācaranti."
msgstr "And they engaged in many forms of improper behavior."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.181"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1754"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu kāsīsu vassaṃvuṭṭho sāvatthiṃ gacchanto bhagavantaṃ dassanāya, yena kīṭāgiri tadavasari."
msgstr "Just then a certain monk who had spent the rainy-season residence in Kāsī was on his way to see the Master at Sāvatthī when he arrived at Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.2"
msgid "Atha kho so bhikkhu pubbaṇ­ha­samayaṃ nivāsetvā patta­cīvara­mādāya kīṭāgiriṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi pāsādikena abhikkantena paṭikkantena ālokitena vilokitena samiñjitena pasāritena okkhittacakkhu iriyā­patha­sam­panno."
msgstr "After dressing in the morning, he took his bowl and robe and entered Kīṭāgiri to collect almsfood. He was pleasing in the way he entered and returned, in looking towards and in looking away, in drawing in and stretching out his arms; his eyes were lowered, and he was perfect in deportment."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.3"
msgid "Manussā taṃ bhikkhuṃ passitvā evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "When people saw him, they said,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.4"
msgid "“kvāyaṃ abalabalo viya mandamando viya bhā­kuṭi­ka­bhā­kuṭiko viya?"
msgstr "“Who is this, acting like a fool, like a dullard, continuously frowning?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.5"
msgid "Ko imassa upagatassa piṇḍakaṃ dassati?"
msgstr "Who will give almsfood to him when he approaches?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:6.6"
msgid "Amhākaṃ pana ayyā assaji­pu­nabba­sukā saṇhā sakhilā sukhasambhāsā mihita­pubbaṅ­gamā ehis­vāga­ta­vādino abbhākuṭikā uttānamukhā pubbabhāsino. Tesaṃ kho nāma piṇḍo dātabbo”ti."
msgstr "Almsfood should instead be given to our Venerables Assaji and Punabbasuka, for they are gentle, congenial, pleasant to speak with, greeting one with a smile, welcoming, friendly, open, the first to speak.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1755"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.1"
msgid "Addasā kho aññataro upāsako taṃ bhikkhuṃ kīṭāgirismiṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ."
msgstr "A certain lay follower saw that monk walking for alms in Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.2"
msgid "Disvāna yena so bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He approached him,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.3"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā taṃ bhikkhuṃ abhivādetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr "bowed down to him, and said,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.4"
msgid "“api, bhante, piṇḍo labbhatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Venerable, have you received any almsfood?”"

#. </p><p><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.319"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.5"
msgid "“Na kho, āvuso, piṇḍo labbhatī”ti."
msgstr "“No, I haven’t.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.6"
msgid "“Ehi, bhante, gharaṃ gamissāmā”ti."
msgstr "“Come, let’s go to my house.”"

#. </p><p><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.4"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.7"
msgid "Atha kho so upāsako taṃ bhikkhuṃ gharaṃ netvā bhojetvā etadavoca—He then said,"
msgstr "He took that monk to his house and gave him a meal."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.8"
msgid "“kahaṃ, bhante, ayyo gamissatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Where are you going, Venerable?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.9"
msgid "“Sāvatthiṃ kho ahaṃ, āvuso, gamissāmi bhagavantaṃ dassanāyā”ti."
msgstr "“I’m going to Sāvatthī to see the Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.10"
msgid "“Tena hi, bhante, mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vanda, evañca vadehi—"
msgstr "“Well then, would you please pay respect at the feet of the Master in my name and say,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.11"
msgid "‘duṭṭho, bhante, kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāso."
msgstr "‘Venerable Sir, the monastery in Kīṭāgiri has been corrupted."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.12"
msgid "Assaji­pu­nabba­sukā nāma kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāsikā alajjino pāpabhikkhū."
msgstr "The bad and shameless monks Assaji and Punabbasuka are staying there."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.13"
msgid "Te evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ ācaranti—"
msgstr "They engage in these kinds of improper behavior:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.14"
msgid "mālāvacchaṃ ropentipi ropāpentipi, siñcantipi siñcāpentipi … pe …"
msgstr "They plant flowering trees, water them …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.15"
msgid "vividhampi anācāraṃ ācaranti."
msgstr "And they engage in many forms of improper behavior."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.16"
msgid "Yepi te, bhante, manussā pubbe saddhā ahesuṃ pasannā tepi etarahi assaddhā appasannā."
msgstr "Those people who previously had faith and confidence have now lost it,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.17"
msgid "Yānipi tāni saṃghassa pubbe dānapathāni tānipi etarahi upacchinnāni."
msgstr "and there’s no longer any support for the monastic Order."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.18"
msgid "Riñcanti pesalā bhikkhū, nivasanti pāpabhikkhū."
msgstr "The good monks have left and the bad monks are staying on."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:7.19"
msgid "Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā kīṭāgiriṃ bhikkhū pahiṇeyya yathāyaṃ kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāso saṇṭhaheyyā’”ti."
msgstr "Venerable Sir, please send monks to stay at the monastery in Kīṭāgiri.’”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.182"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.5"></a> <a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1756"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.1"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho so bhikkhu tassa upāsakassa paṭissutvā yena sāvatthi tena pakkāmi."
msgstr "The monk consented and left for Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.2"
msgid "Anupubbena yena sāvatthi jetavanaṃ anātha­piṇḍi­kassa ārāmo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "When he eventually arrived at Sāvatthī, he went to the Master in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.3"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr "He bowed down to the Master and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.4"
msgid "Āciṇṇaṃ kho panetaṃ buddhānaṃ bhagavantānaṃ āgantukehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ paṭisammodituṃ."
msgstr "It is the custom for Buddhas to greet visiting monks,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.5"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā taṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and so the Master said to him,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.6"
msgid "“kacci, bhikkhu, khamanīyaṃ kacci yāpanīyaṃ,"
msgstr "“I hope you’re keeping well, monk, I hope you’re comfortable;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.7"
msgid "“kaccisi appa­kila­ma­thena addhānaṃ āgato,"
msgstr "I hope you’re not tired from traveling."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.8"
msgid "kuto ca tvaṃ, bhikkhu, āgacchasī”ti?"
msgstr "Where have you come from?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.9"
msgid "“Khamanīyaṃ, bhagavā, yāpanīyaṃ, bhagavā."
msgstr "“I’m keeping well, Master, I’m comfortable;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.10"
msgid "Appa­kila­ma­thena cāhaṃ, bhante, addhānaṃ āgato."
msgstr "I’m not tired from traveling.”"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.320"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.11"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, bhante, kāsīsu vassaṃvuṭṭho sāvatthiṃ āgacchanto bhagavantaṃ dassanāya yena kīṭāgiri tadavasariṃ."
msgstr "He then told the Master all that had happened at Kīṭāgiri"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.12"
msgid "Atha khvāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇ­ha­samayaṃ nivāsetvā patta­cīvara­mādāya kīṭāgiriṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.13"
msgid "Addasā kho maṃ, bhante, aññataro upāsako kīṭāgirismiṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.14"
msgid "Disvāna yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.15"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.16"
msgid "‘api, bhante, piṇḍo labbhatī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.17"
msgid "‘Na kho, āvuso, piṇḍo labbhatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.18"
msgid "‘Ehi, bhante, gharaṃ gamissāmā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.19"
msgid "Atha kho, bhante, so upāsako maṃ gharaṃ netvā bhojetvā etadavoca—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.20"
msgid "‘kahaṃ, bhante, ayyo gamissatī’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.21"
msgid "‘Sāvatthiṃ kho ahaṃ, āvuso, gamissāmi bhagavantaṃ dassanāyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.22"
msgid "Tena hi, bhante, mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vanda, evañca vadehi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.23"
msgid "‘duṭṭho, bhante, kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāso, assaji­pu­nabba­sukā nāma kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāsikā alajjino pāpabhikkhū."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.24"
msgid "Te evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ ācaranti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.25"
msgid "mālāvacchaṃ ropentipi ropāpentipi, siñcantipi siñcāpentipi … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.26"
msgid "vividhampi anācāraṃ ācaranti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.27"
msgid "Yepi te, bhante, manussā pubbe saddhā ahesuṃ pasannā tepi etarahi assaddhā appasannā, yānipi tāni saṃghassa pubbe dānapathāni tānipi etarahi upacchinnāni, riñcanti pesalā bhikkhū nivasanti pāpabhikkhū."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.28"
msgid "Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā kīṭāgiriṃ bhikkhū pahiṇeyya yathāyaṃ kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāso saṇṭhaheyyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:8.29"
msgid "Tato ahaṃ, bhagavā, āgacchāmī”ti."
msgstr "and finished by saying, “Master, that’s where I’ve come from.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1757"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etasmiṃ nidāne etasmiṃ pakaraṇe bhikkhusaṃghaṃ sannipātāpetvā bhikkhū paṭipucchi—"
msgstr "The Master then had the Order of monks assembled and asked them,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.2"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira, bhikkhave, assaji­pu­nabba­sukā nāma kīṭāgirismiṃ āvāsikā alajjino pāpabhikkhū te evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ ācaranti—mālāvacchaṃ ropentipi ropāpentipi, siñcantipi siñcāpentipi … pe … vividhampi anācāraṃ ācaranti,"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that the bad and shameless monks Assaji and Punabbasuka are engaging in such kinds of improper behavior at Kīṭāgiri?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.3"
msgid "yepi te, bhikkhave, manussā pubbe saddhā ahesuṃ pasannā tepi etarahi assaddhā appasannā;"
msgstr "And is it true that those people who previously had faith and confidence have now lost it,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.4"
msgid "yānipi tāni saṃghassa pubbe dānapathāni tānipi etarahi upacchinnāni;"
msgstr "that there’s no longer any support for the monastic Order,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.5"
msgid "riñcanti pesalā bhikkhū nivasanti pāpabhikkhū”ti?"
msgstr "and that the good monks have left and the bad monks are staying on?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.6"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.7"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha criticized them …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.8"
msgid "kathañhi nāma te, bhikkhave, moghapurisā evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ ācarissanti—"
msgstr "“Monks, how can those foolish men engage in such kinds of improper behavior?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.9"
msgid "mālāvacchaṃ ropessantipi ropāpessantipi, sañcissantipi siñ­cā­pes­santipi, ocinissantipi ocinā­pes­santipi, ganthissantipi ganthā­pes­santipi, ekato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, ubhato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, mañjarikaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, vidhūtikaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, vaṭaṃsakaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, āveḷaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi, uracchadaṃ karissantipi kārāpessantipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.10"
msgid "Te kulitthīnaṃ kuladhītānaṃ kulakumārīnaṃ kulasuṇhānaṃ kuladāsīnaṃ ekato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, ubhato­vaṇ­ṭika­mālaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, mañjarikaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, vidhūtikaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, vaṭaṃsakaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, āveḷaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi, uracchadaṃ harissantipi hārāpessantipi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.11"
msgid "Te kulitthīhi kuladhītāhi kulakumārīhi kulasuṇhāhi kuladāsīhi saddhiṃ ekabhājanepi bhuñjissanti, ekathālakepi pivissanti, ekāsanepi nisīdissanti, ekamañcepi tuvaṭṭissanti, ekattharaṇāpi tuvaṭṭissanti, ekapāvuraṇāpi tuvaṭṭissanti, ekattha­ra­ṇa­pāvu­raṇāpi tuvaṭṭissanti, vikālepi bhuñjissanti, majjampi pivissanti, mālā­gandha­vi­lepa­nampi dhārissanti, naccissantipi gāyissantipi vādessantipi lāsessantipi, naccantiyāpi naccissanti naccantiyāpi gāyissanti naccantiyāpi vādessanti naccantiyāpi lāsessanti, gāyantiyāpi naccissanti gāyantiyāpi gāyissanti gāyantiyāpi vādessanti gāyantiyāpi lāsessanti, vādentiyāpi naccissanti vādentiyāpi gāyissanti vādentiyāpi vādessanti vādentiyāpi lāsessanti, lāsentiyāpi naccissanti lāsentiyāpi gāyissanti lāsentiyāpi vādessanti lāsentiyāpi lāsessanti, aṭṭhapadepi kīḷissanti dasapadepi kīḷissanti, ākāsepi kīḷissanti, pari­hāra­pa­thepi kīḷissanti, santikāyapi kīḷissanti, khalikāyapi kīḷissanti, ghaṭikāyapi kīḷissanti, salāka­hat­thenapi kīḷissanti, akkhenapi kīḷissanti, paṅgacīrenapi kīḷissanti, vaṅkakenapi kīḷissanti, mokkhacikāyapi kīḷissanti, ciṅgulakenapi kīḷissanti, pattāḷhakenapi kīḷissanti, rathakenapi kīḷissanti, dhanukenapi kīḷissanti, akkharikāyapi kīḷissanti, manesikāyapi kīḷissanti, yathāvajjenapi kīḷissanti, hatthismimpi sikkhissanti, assasmimpi sikkhissanti, rathasmimpi sikkhissanti, dhanusmimpi sikkhissanti, tharusmimpi sikkhissanti, hatthissapi purato dhāvissanti, assassapi purato dhāvissanti, rathassapi purato dhāvissantipi ādhāvissantipi, usseḷessantipi, apphoṭes­santipi, nib­bujjhis­santipi, muṭṭhīhipi yujjhissanti, raṅgamajjhepi saṅghāṭiṃ pattharitvā naccakiṃ evaṃ vakkhanti “idha, bhagini, naccassū”ti nalāṭikampi dassanti, vividhampi anācāraṃ ācarissanti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.321"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.12"
msgid "Netaṃ, bhikkhave, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …” …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.13"
msgid "vigarahitvā dhammiṃ kathaṃ katvā sāri­putta­mog­gallāne āmantesi—"
msgstr "After criticizing them, he gave a teaching and then addressed Sāriputta and Moggallāna,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.14"
msgid "“gacchatha tumhe, sāriputtā, kīṭāgiriṃ gantvā assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ karotha."
msgstr "“Sāriputta, the two of you should go and do a formal procedure to banish the monks Assaji and Punabbasuka from Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:9.15"
msgid "Tumhākaṃ ete saddhivihārikā”ti."
msgstr "They are your students.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.183"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1758"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.1"
msgid "“Kathaṃ mayaṃ, bhante, assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ karoma?"
msgstr "“Venerable Sir, how can we do a formal procedure to banish these monks from Kīṭāgiri?"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.2"
msgid "Caṇḍā te bhikkhū pharusā”ti."
msgstr "They are temperamental and harsh.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.3"
msgid "“Tena hi tumhe, sāriputtā, bahukehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ gacchathā”ti."
msgstr "“Well, take many monks.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho sāri­putta­mog­gallānā bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Ok.”"

#. </p><p><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.7"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.5"
msgid "“Evañca pana, bhikkhave, kātabbaṃ."
msgstr "“And, monks, this is how it should be done."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ assaji­pu­nabba­sukā bhikkhū codetabbā."
msgstr "First you should accuse the monks Assaji and Punabbasuka."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.7"
msgid "Codetvā sāretabbā."
msgstr "They should then be made to confess what they have done,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.8"
msgid "Sāretvā āpattiṃ ropetabbā."
msgstr "before they’re declared guilty of an offense."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:10.9"
msgid "Āpattiṃ ropetvā byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṃgho ñāpetabbo—"
msgstr "A competent and capable monk should then inform the Order:"

#. </p><div class="kamma"><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1759"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.1"
msgid "‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "‘Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.322"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.2"
msgid "Ime assaji­pu­nabba­sukā bhikkhū kuladūsakā pāpasamācārā."
msgstr "These monks Assaji and Punabbasuka are corrupters of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.3"
msgid "Imesaṃ pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Their bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.4"
msgid "Kulāni ca imehi duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by them are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.5"
msgid "Yadi saṃghassa pattakallaṃ, saṃgho assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ kareyya—“na assaji­pu­nabba­sukehi bhikkhūhi kīṭāgirismiṃ vatthabban”ti."
msgstr "If it seems appropriate to the Order, the Order should do a formal procedure to banish them from Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:11.6"
msgid "Esā ñatti."
msgstr "This is the motion."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1760"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.1"
msgid "Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.2"
msgid "Ime assaji­pu­nabba­sukā bhikkhū kuladūsakā pāpasamācārā."
msgstr "These monks Assaji and Punabbasuka are corrupters of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.3"
msgid "Imesaṃ pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Their bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.4"
msgid "Kulāni ca imehi duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by them are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.5"
msgid "Saṃgho assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ karoti—"
msgstr "The Order is doing a formal procedure to banish them,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.6"
msgid "“na assaji­pu­nabba­sukehi bhikkhūhi kīṭāgirismiṃ vatthabban”ti."
msgstr "declaring that the monks Assaji and Punabbasuka cannot stay at Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.7"
msgid "Yassāyasmato khamati assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammassa karaṇaṃ—“na assaji­pu­nabba­sukehi bhikkhūhi kīṭāgirismiṃ vatthabban”ti, so tuṇhassa;"
msgstr "Any monk who approves of doing a formal procedure to banish them from Kīṭāgiri should remain silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:12.8"
msgid "yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya."
msgstr "Any monk who does not approve should say so."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1761"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:13.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi … pe …"
msgstr "A second time …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:13.2"
msgid "tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I speak on this matter."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:13.3"
msgid "suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho … pe …"
msgstr "Venerables, let the Order listen to me. …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:13.4"
msgid "so bhāseyya."
msgstr "should say so."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1762"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:14.1"
msgid "Kataṃ saṃghena assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ—"
msgstr "The Order has performed the formal procedure to banish them,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:14.2"
msgid "“na assaji­pu­nabba­sukehi bhikkhūhi kīṭāgirismiṃ vatthabban”ti."
msgstr "declaring that Assaji and Punabbasuka cannot stay at Kīṭāgiri."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:14.3"
msgid "Khamati saṃghassa, tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "The Order approves and is therefore silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:14.4"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.’”"

#. </p></div><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.184"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.1.8"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1763"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.1"
msgid "Atha kho sāri­putta­mog­gallā­nappa­mukho bhikkhusaṃgho kīṭāgiriṃ gantvā assa­ji­punab­basukā­naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kīṭāgirismā pab­bājanī­ya­kammaṃ akāsi—“na assaji­pu­nabba­sukehi bhikkhūhi kīṭāgirismiṃ vatthabban”ti."
msgstr "Soon afterwards an Order of monks headed by Sāriputta and Moggallāna went there and did the formal procedure to banish those monks from Kīṭāgiri."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.323"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.2"
msgid "Te saṃghena pab­bājanī­ya­kamma­katā na sammā vattanti, na lomaṃ pātenti, na netthāraṃ vattanti, na bhikkhū khamāpenti,"
msgstr "After the Order had performed the formal procedure, those monks did not behave properly or suitably so as to deserve to be cleared, nor did they ask the monks for forgiveness."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.3"
msgid "akkosanti paribhāsanti chandagāmitā dosagāmitā mohagāmitā bhayagāmitā pāpenti,"
msgstr "Instead they abused and reviled them, and they defamed them as acting from desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.4"
msgid "pakkamantipi, vibbhamantipi."
msgstr "And they left and they disrobed."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.5"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.6"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.324"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:15.7"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma assaji­pu­nabba­sukā bhikkhū saṃghena pab­bājanī­ya­kamma­katā na sammā vattissanti, na lomaṃ pātessanti, na netthāraṃ vattissanti, na bhikkhū khamāpessanti, akkosissanti pari­bhāsis­santi, chandagāmitā dosagāmitā mohagāmitā bhayagāmitā pāpessanti pakka­mis­santipi vib­bha­mis­santipī”ti."
msgstr "“When the Order has performed a formal procedure to banish them, how can these monks act in this way?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1764"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.1"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū assaji­pu­nabba­suke bhikkhū aneka­pariyā­yena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They rebuked the monks Assaji and Punabbasuka in many ways and then informed the Master. …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.2"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira, bhikkhave, assaji­pu­nabba­sukā bhikkhū saṃghena pab­bājanī­ya­kamma­katā na sammā vattanti … pe …"
msgstr "He said, “Is it true, monks, that when the Order had performed a formal procedure to banish them, the monks Assaji and Punabbasuka did not act properly …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.3"
msgid "vibbhamantipī”ti?"
msgstr "and they disrobed?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.4"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.5"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha criticized them …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:16.6"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "“And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1765"></a><strong class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.2"
msgid "“Bhikkhu paneva aññataraṃ gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vā upanissāya viharati kuladūsako pāpasamācāro."
msgstr "‘If a monk who lives supported by a village or town is a corrupter of families and badly behaved,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.3"
msgid "Tassa kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca, kulāni ca tena duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and his bad behavior is seen and heard about, and the families corrupted by him are seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.4"
msgid "So bhikkhu bhikkhūhi evamassa vacanīyo—"
msgstr "then the monks should correct him in this way:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.5"
msgid "‘āyasmā kho kuladūsako pāpasamācāro,"
msgstr "“Venerable, you’re a corrupter of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.6"
msgid "āyasmato kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca, kulāni cāyasmatā duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Your bad behavior is seen and heard about, and the families corrupted by you are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.7"
msgid "Pakkamatāyasmā imamhā āvāsā."
msgstr "Leave this monastery;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.8"
msgid "Alaṃ te idha vāsenā’ti."
msgstr "you have stayed here long enough.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.9"
msgid "Evañca so bhikkhu bhikkhūhi vuccamāno te bhikkhū evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If he replies,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.10"
msgid "‘chandagāmino ca bhikkhū dosagāmino ca bhikkhū mohagāmino ca bhikkhū bhayagāmino ca bhikkhū tādisikāya āpattiyā ekaccaṃ pabbājenti ekaccaṃ na pabbājentī’ti,"
msgstr "“You’re acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear; because of this sort of offense, you banish some, but not others,”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.11"
msgid "so bhikkhu bhikkhūhi evamassa vacanīyo—"
msgstr "the monks should correct him in this way:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.12"
msgid "‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca."
msgstr "“Venerable, don’t say that."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.13"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū chandagāmino."
msgstr "The monks are not acting out of desire,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.14"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū dosagāmino."
msgstr "ill-will,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.15"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū mohagāmino."
msgstr "confusion,"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.325"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.16"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū bhayagāmino."
msgstr "and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.17"
msgid "Āyasmā kho kuladūsako pāpasamācāro."
msgstr "Venerable, you’re a corrupter of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.18"
msgid "Āyasmato kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Your bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.19"
msgid "Kulāni cāyasmatā duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by you are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.20"
msgid "Pakkamatāyasmā imamhā āvāsā."
msgstr "Venerable, leave this monastery;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.21"
msgid "Alaṃ te idha vāsenā’ti."
msgstr "you have stayed here long enough.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.22"
msgid "Evañca so bhikkhu bhikkhūhi vuccamāno tatheva paggaṇheyya, so bhikkhu bhikkhūhi yāvatatiyaṃ sama­nubhā­si­tabbo tassa paṭinissaggāya."
msgstr "If that monk still continues as before, the monks should admonish him up to three times to make him stop."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.23"
msgid "Yāvatatiyañce sama­nubhā­si­yamāno taṃ paṭi­nissaj­jeyya, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ;"
msgstr "If he then stops, that is good."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.24"
msgid "no ce paṭi­nissaj­jeyya, saṃghādiseso”ti."
msgstr "If not, he commits an offense entailing suspension.’”"

#. </strong> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:17.25"
msgid "(<em>13</em>:<strong>17</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:18.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1766"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:18.2"
msgid "Bhikkhu paneva aññataraṃ gāmaṃ vā nigamaṃ vāti"
msgstr "A monk […] a village or town:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:18.3"
msgid "gāmopi nigamopi nagarampi gāmo ceva nigamo ca."
msgstr "a village and a town and a city are included in just a village and a town."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1767"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:19.1"
msgid "Upanissāya viharatīti"
msgstr "Lives supported by:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:19.2"
msgid "tattha paṭibaddhā honti cīvara­piṇḍa­pāta­se­nāsa­na­gilā­nappac­caya­bhesaj­ja­parik­khārā."
msgstr "robes, almsfood, lodging requisites, and medicines can be obtained in that place."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.185"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1768"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:20.1"
msgid "Kulaṃ nāma"
msgstr "A family:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:20.2"
msgid "cattāri kulāni—"
msgstr "there are four kinds of families:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:20.3"
msgid "khattiyakulaṃ, brāhmaṇakulaṃ, vessakulaṃ, suddakulaṃ."
msgstr "aristocratic families, brahmin families, merchant families, worker families."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1769"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:21.1"
msgid "Kuladūsakoti"
msgstr "A corrupter of families:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:21.2"
msgid "kulāni dūseti pupphena vā phalena vā cuṇṇena vā mattikāya vā dantakaṭṭhena vā veḷuyā vā vejjikāya vā jaṅgha­pe­sani­kena vā."
msgstr "he corrupts families by means of flowers, fruit, bath powder, soap, toothbrushes, bamboo, medical treatment, or by taking messages on foot."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1770"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.326"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:22.1"
msgid "Pāpasamācāroti"
msgstr "Badly behaved:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:22.2"
msgid "mālāvacchaṃ ropetipi ropāpetipi,"
msgstr "he plants flowering trees and gets it done;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:22.3"
msgid "siñcatipi siñcāpetipi,"
msgstr "he waters them and gets it done;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:22.4"
msgid "ocinātipi ocināpetipi,"
msgstr "he plucks them and gets it done;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:22.5"
msgid "ganthetipi ganthāpetipi."
msgstr "he ties the flowers together and gets it done."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1771"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:23.1"
msgid "Dissanti ceva suyyanti cāti"
msgstr "Is seen and heard about:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:23.2"
msgid "ye saṃmukhā te passanti,"
msgstr "those who are present see it;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:23.3"
msgid "ye tirokkhā te suṇanti."
msgstr "those who are absent hear about it."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1772"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:24.1"
msgid "Kulāni ca tena duṭṭhānīti"
msgstr "The families corrupted by him:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:24.2"
msgid "pubbe saddhā hutvā taṃ āgamma assaddhā honti,"
msgstr "they have lost their faith because of him;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:24.3"
msgid "pasannā hutvā appasannā honti."
msgstr "they have lost their confidence because of him."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="21"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1773"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:25.1"
msgid "Dissanti ceva suyyanti cāti"
msgstr "Are seen and heard about:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:25.2"
msgid "ye saṃmukhā te passanti,"
msgstr "those who are present see it;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:25.3"
msgid "ye tirokkhā te suṇanti."
msgstr "those who are absent hear about it."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1774"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:26.1"
msgid "So bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Him:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:26.2"
msgid "yo so kuladūsako bhikkhu."
msgstr "that monk who is a corrupter of families."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1775"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.1"
msgid "Bhikkhūhīti"
msgstr "The monks:"

#. </strong></p><div class="gloss"><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.2"
msgid "aññehi bhikkhūhi."
msgstr "Other monks,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.3"
msgid "Ye passanti ye suṇanti."
msgstr "those who see it or hear about it."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.4"
msgid "Tehi vattabbo—"
msgstr "They should say,"

#. <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.5"
msgid "“āyasmā kho kuladūsako pāpasamācāro."
msgstr "“Venerable, you’re a corrupter of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.6"
msgid "Āyasmato kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Your bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.7"
msgid "Kulāni cāyasmatā duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by you are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.8"
msgid "Pakkamatāyasmā imamhā āvāsā."
msgstr "Leave this monastery;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:27.9"
msgid "Alaṃ te idha vāsenā”ti."
msgstr "you have stayed here long enough.”"

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1776"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:28.1"
msgid "Evañca so bhikkhu bhikkhūhi vuccamāno te bhikkhū evaṃ vadeyya—"
msgstr "If he replies,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:28.2"
msgid "“chandagāmino ca bhikkhū, dosagāmino ca bhikkhū, mohagāmino ca bhikkhū, bhayagāmino ca bhikkhū."
msgstr "“You’re acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:28.3"
msgid "Tādisikāya āpattiyā ekaccaṃ pabbājenti ekaccaṃ na pabbājentī”ti."
msgstr "because of this sort of offense, you banish some, but not others.”"

#. </p></div><p><a class="sc" id="25"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1777"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:29.1"
msgid "So bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Him:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:29.2"
msgid "yo so kammakato bhikkhu."
msgstr "that monk who is having a formal procedure done against him."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="26"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1778"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:30.1"
msgid "Bhikkhūhīti"
msgstr "The monks:"

#. </strong></p><div class="gloss"><p><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1779"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:30.2"
msgid "aññehi bhikkhūhi."
msgstr "Other monks,"

#. <a class="sc" id="27"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.1"
msgid "Ye passanti ye suṇanti tehi vattabbo—"
msgstr "those who see it or hear about it. They should say,"

#. <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.2"
msgid "“māyasmā evaṃ avaca."
msgstr "“Venerable, don’t say that."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.3"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū chandagāmino, na ca bhikkhū dosagāmino, na ca bhikkhū mohagāmino, na ca bhikkhū bhayagāmino."
msgstr "The monks are not acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.4"
msgid "Āyasmā kho kuladūsako pāpasamācāro."
msgstr "Venerable, you’re a corrupter of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.5"
msgid "Āyasmato kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Your bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.6"
msgid "Kulāni cāyasmatā duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by you are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.7"
msgid "Pakkamatāyasmā imamhā āvāsā."
msgstr "Venerable, leave this monastery;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.8"
msgid "Alaṃ te idha vāsenā”ti."
msgstr "you have stayed here long enough.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.9"
msgid "Dutiyampi vattabbo."
msgstr "And they should say this a second"

#. <a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1780"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:31.10"
msgid "Tatiyampi vattabbo."
msgstr "and a third time."

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="28"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.1"
msgid "Sace paṭinissajjati, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ."
msgstr "If he stops, that is good."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.2"
msgid "No ce paṭinissajjati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he does not stop, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. <span class="subrule"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.3"
msgid "Sutvā na vadanti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If those who hear about it do not say anything, they commit an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </span>
#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.4"
msgid "So bhikkhu saṃgha­majjhampi ākaḍḍhitvā vattabbo—"
msgstr "That monk, even if he has to be dragged into the middle of the Order of monks, should be corrected in this way:"

#. <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.5"
msgid "“māyasmā evaṃ avaca."
msgstr "“Venerable, don’t say that."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.6"
msgid "Na ca bhikkhū chandagāmino, na ca bhikkhū dosagāmino, na ca bhikkhū mohagāmino, na ca bhikkhū bhayagāmino."
msgstr "The monks are not acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.7"
msgid "Āyasmā kho kuladūsako pāpasamācāro."
msgstr "Venerable, you’re a corrupter of families and badly behaved."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.8"
msgid "Āyasmato kho pāpakā samācārā dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "Your bad behavior is seen and heard about,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.9"
msgid "Kulāni cāyasmatā duṭṭhāni dissanti ceva suyyanti ca."
msgstr "and the families corrupted by you are seen and heard about."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.10"
msgid "Pakkamatāyasmā imamhā āvāsā."
msgstr "Venerable, leave this monastery;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.11"
msgid "Alaṃ te idha vāsenā”ti."
msgstr "you have stayed here long enough.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.12"
msgid "Dutiyampi vattabbo."
msgstr "They should say this a second"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.13"
msgid "Tatiyampi vattabbo."
msgstr "and a third time."

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.14"
msgid "Sace paṭinissajjati, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ."
msgstr "If he stops, that is good."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.15"
msgid "No ce paṭinissajjati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he does not stop, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p></div><p><strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:32.16"
msgid "So bhikkhu sama­nubhā­si­tabbo."
msgstr "Should admonish him:"

#. </strong>
#. </p><div class="gloss"><p><a class="sc" id="29"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1781"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:33.1"
msgid "“Evañca pana, bhikkhave, sama­nubhā­si­tabbo."
msgstr "“And, monks, he should be admonished in this way."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:33.2"
msgid "Byattena bhikkhunā paṭibalena saṃgho ñāpetabbo—"
msgstr "A competent and capable monk should inform the Order:"

#. </p><div class="kamma"><p><a class="sc" id="30"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1782"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:34.1"
msgid "‘Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "‘Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.327"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:34.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ itthannāmo bhikkhu saṃghena pab­bājanī­ya­kamma­kato bhikkhū chandagāmitā dosagāmitā mohagāmitā bhayagāmitā pāpeti."
msgstr "This monk so-and-so, who has had a formal procedure of banishment done against him, is defaming the monks as acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:34.3"
msgid "So taṃ vatthuṃ na paṭinissajjati."
msgstr "And he keeps on doing it."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:34.4"
msgid "Yadi saṃghassa pattakallaṃ, saṃgho itthannāmaṃ bhikkhuṃ samanubhāseyya tassa vatthussa paṭinissaggāya."
msgstr "If it seems appropriate to the Order, the Order should admonish him to make him stop."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:34.5"
msgid "Esā ñatti."
msgstr "This is the motion."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1783"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.1"
msgid "Suṇātu me, bhante, saṃgho."
msgstr "Venerables, let the Order listen to me."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ itthannāmo bhikkhu saṃghena pab­bājanī­ya­kamma­kato bhikkhū chandagāmitā dosagāmitā mohagāmitā bhayagāmitā pāpeti."
msgstr "This monk so-and-so, who has had a formal procedure of banishment done against him, is defaming the monks as acting out of desire, ill-will, confusion, and fear."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.3"
msgid "So taṃ vatthuṃ na paṭinissajjati."
msgstr "And he keeps on doing it."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.4"
msgid "Saṃgho itthannāmaṃ bhikkhuṃ samanubhāsati tassa vatthussa paṭinissaggāya."
msgstr "The Order admonishes him to make him stop."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.5"
msgid "Yassāyasmato khamati itthannāmassa bhikkhuno samanubhāsanā tassa vatthussa paṭinissaggāya, so tuṇhassa;"
msgstr "Any monk who approves of admonishing him to make him stop should remain silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:35.6"
msgid "yassa nakkhamati, so bhāseyya."
msgstr "Any monk who does not approve should say so."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1784"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:36.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi … pe …"
msgstr "A second time I speak on this matter …"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:36.2"
msgid "tatiyampi etamatthaṃ vadāmi … pe …."
msgstr "A third time I speak on this matter …"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1785"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:37.1"
msgid "Samanubhaṭṭho saṃghena itthannāmo bhikkhu tassa vatthussa paṭinissaggāya."
msgstr "This monk so-and-so has been admonished by the Order to make him stop."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:37.2"
msgid "Khamati saṃghassa, tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "The Order approves and is therefore silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:37.3"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmī’”ti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.’”"

#. </p></div></div><hr><p><a class="sc" id="34"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1786"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:38.1"
msgid "Ñattiyā dukkaṭaṃ,"
msgstr "After the motion, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:38.2"
msgid "dvīhi kammavācāhi thullaccayā,"
msgstr "After each of the first two announcements, he commits a serious offense."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:38.3"
msgid "kamma­vācā­pari­yosāne āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "When the last announcement is finished, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:38.4"
msgid "Saṃghādisesaṃ ajjhā­pajjan­tassa ñattiyā dukkaṭaṃ, dvīhi kammavācāhi thullaccayā paṭippas­sam­bhanti."
msgstr "For one who commits the offense entailing suspension, the offense of wrong conduct and the serious offenses are annulled."

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="35"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.186"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1787"></a>
#. <strong class="term"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.1"
msgid "Saṃghādisesoti"
msgstr "He commits an offense entailing suspension:"

#. </strong><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.2"
msgid "saṃghova tassā āpattiyā parivāsaṃ deti, mūlāya paṭikassati, mānattaṃ deti, abbheti;"
msgstr "only the monastic Order gives probation for that offense, sends back to the beginning, places under deference, and rehabilitates—"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.3"
msgid "na sambahulā, na ekapuggalo."
msgstr "not several monks, not an individual."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.4"
msgid "Tena vuccati—"
msgstr "Therefore it is called"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.5"
msgid "“saṃghādiseso”ti,"
msgstr "“an offense entailing suspension.”"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.6"
msgid "tasseva āpatti­nikāyassa nāmakammaṃ adhivacanaṃ."
msgstr "This is the name and designation of this class of offense."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:39.7"
msgid "Tenapi vuccati “saṃghādiseso”ti."
msgstr "Therefore, too, it is called “an offense entailing suspension.”"

#. </span>
#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:40.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-ss.13.3"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.3.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1788"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:40.2"
msgid "Dhammakamme dhamma­kamma­saññī na paṭinissajjati, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If it is a legitimate procedure, and he perceives it as legitimate, but he does not stop, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="37"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1789"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:41.1"
msgid "Dhammakamme vematiko na paṭinissajjati, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If it is a legitimate procedure, but he is unsure if it is, and he does not stop, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1790"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:42.1"
msgid "Dhammakamme adhamma­kamma­saññī na paṭinissajjati, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr "If it is a legitimate procedure, but he perceives it as illegitimate, and he does not stop, he commits an offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1791"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:43.1"
msgid "Adhammakamme dhamma­kamma­saññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it is an illegitimate procedure, but he perceives it as legitimate, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1792"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:44.1"
msgid "Adhammakamme vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it is an illegitimate procedure, but he is unsure if it is, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1793"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:45.1"
msgid "Adhammakamme adhamma­kamma­saññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If it is an illegitimate procedure, and he perceives it as illegitimate, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.1"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.13.3.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1794"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.2"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.3"
msgid "asama­nu­bhāsan­tassa,"
msgstr "if he has not been admonished;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.4"
msgid "paṭi­nissaj­jan­tassa,"
msgstr "if he stops;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.5"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:46.6"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="43"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1795"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:47.1"
msgid "Kula­dūsaka­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ terasamaṃ."
msgstr "The thirteenth rule, the training rule on corrupters of families, is finished."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.328"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1796"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.1"
msgid "“Uddiṭṭhā kho, āyasmanto, terasa saṃghādisesā dhammā, nava paṭhamāpattikā, cattāro yāvatatiyakā."
msgstr "“Venerables, the thirteen rules entailing suspension have been recited, nine being immediate offenses, four after the third announcement."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.2"
msgid "Yesaṃ bhikkhu aññataraṃ vā aññataraṃ vā āpajjitvā yāvatīhaṃ jānaṃ paṭicchādeti tāvatīhaṃ tena bhikkhunā akāmā parivattabbaṃ."
msgstr "If a monk commits any one of them, he is to undergo probation for the same number of days as he knowingly concealed that offense."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.3"
msgid "Pari­vuttha­pari­vāsena bhikkhunā uttari chārattaṃ ­bhik­khu­mānattāya paṭi­pajji­tabbaṃ."
msgstr "When this is completed, he must practice deference for a further six days."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.4"
msgid "Ciṇṇamānatto bhikkhu yattha siyā vīsatigaṇo bhikkhusaṃgho tattha so bhikkhu abbhetabbo."
msgstr "When this is completed, he is to be rehabilitated wherever there is an Order of at least twenty monks."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.5"
msgid "Ekenapi ce ūno vīsatigaṇo bhikkhusaṃgho taṃ bhikkhuṃ abbheyya, so ca bhikkhu anabbhito, te ca bhikkhū gārayhā,"
msgstr "If that monk is rehabilitated by an Order of even one less than twenty, that monk is not rehabilitated and those monks are at fault."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.6"
msgid "ayaṃ tattha sāmīci."
msgstr "This is the proper procedure."

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.7"
msgid "Tatthāyasmante pucchāmi—"
msgstr "In regard to this I ask you,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.8"
msgid "‘kaccittha parisuddhā’?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.9"
msgid "Dutiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A second time I ask,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.10"
msgid "‘kaccittha parisuddhā’?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.11"
msgid "Tatiyampi pucchāmi—"
msgstr "A third time I ask,"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.12"
msgid "‘kaccittha parisuddhā’?"
msgstr "‘Are you pure in this?’"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.13"
msgid "Pari­sud­dhet­thā­yasmanto."
msgstr "You are pure in this"

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.14"
msgid "Tasmā tuṇhī,"
msgstr "and therefore silent."

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:48.15"
msgid "evametaṃ dhārayāmī”ti."
msgstr "I will remember it thus.”"

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="45"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1797"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:49.1"
msgid "Terasakaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The group of thirteen is finished."

#. </p><p class="endsection summary"><a class="sc" id="46"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1798"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:50.1"
msgid "Tassuddānaṃ"
msgstr "This is the summary:"

#. </p><div class="uddana"><p><a class="sc" id="47"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1799"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:51.1"
msgid "Vissaṭṭhi kāyasaṃsaggaṃ,"
msgstr "Emission, physical contact,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:51.2"
msgid "duṭṭhullaṃ attakāmañca;"
msgstr "Lewd, and his own needs;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:51.3"
msgid "Sañcarittaṃ kuṭī ceva,"
msgstr "Mediation, and a hut,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:51.4"
msgid "vihāro ca amūlakaṃ."
msgstr "And a dwelling, groundlessly."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="48"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.329"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1800"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:52.1"
msgid "Kiñcilesañca bhedo ca,"
msgstr "A pretext, and schism,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:52.2"
msgid "tasseva anuvattakā;"
msgstr "Those who agree with him;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:52.3"
msgid "Dubbacaṃ kuladūsañca,"
msgstr "Difficult to correct, and corrupters of families:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:52.4"
msgid "saṃghādisesā terasāti."
msgstr "The thirteen offenses entailing suspension."

#. </p></div><p class="endsection"><a class="sc" id="49"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1801"></a> 
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-ss13:53.1"
msgid "Saṃ­ghādi­sesa­kaṇḍaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "The chapter on offenses entailing suspension is finished."

